[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Genspark chat bookmark privacy policy public private View Let me search more specifically for Genspark's official privacy policy and terms of service to get you the exact information about bookmark privacy: Using Tool | Search site:genspark.ai privacy policy terms of service bookmarks View Let me try to find the official Genspark privacy policy directly: Using Tool | Search \"genspark.ai\" privacy policy official View Let me check the official MainFunc.ai privacy policy since that appears to be Genspark's parent company: Using Tool | Read https://mainfunc.ai/privacy View Based on my research of Genspark's official privacy policy, I can provide you with a clear answer about your bookmark privacy concerns: Your Bookmarked Chats Are Private and Not Publicly Visible Here's what the privacy policy confirms: Privacy Protection for Your Content Personal Account Data: Your bookmarks are part of your personal account data and remain private to you only No Public Sharing: Genspark explicitly states they do not sell, trade, or share personal data with third parties except in very specific circumstances (like legal requirements or with your explicit consent) Account Security: Your data is stored securely with access controls that restrict viewing to your account only What This Means for Your Bookmarks: Aspect\tStatus\tDetails Visibility\tPrivate Only\tOnly you can see your bookmarked chats when logged into your account Public Access\tNo\tBookmarks are not indexed by search engines or visible to other users Data Sharing\tNot Shared\tGenspark doesn't share your bookmark data with third parties Account Protection\tSecured\tProtected by your login credentials and Genspark's security measures Key Privacy Safeguards: ✅ Individual Account Control - Your bookmarks are tied to your personal account ✅ No Public Database - Bookmarked content isn't added to any public repository ✅ User Consent Required - Any sharing would require your explicit permission ✅ Data Deletion Rights - You can delete your account and data within 30 days if desired Recommendation: Your privacy concern is valid, and based on Genspark's privacy policy, your bookmarked chats will remain completely private to your account. However, for maximum peace of mind: Regular Review - Periodically review what you've bookmarked Account Security - Use strong, unique passwords for your Genspark account Privacy Settings - Check your account settings for any additional privacy controls The privacy policy is comprehensive and follows standard data protection practices, giving you control over your personal information including bookmarked conversations. Privacy Policy Source Super Agent Hire an AI today Free Now +13 Ultra Speak"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Source: "},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=f7754132-70dc-483b-8b5c-da35e8540810","children":[{"text":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=f7754132-70dc-483b-8b5c-da35e8540810"}]}]}]
